OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FThe Irish army has been called in to
OL,7,Fremove heavy vehicles blocking fuel
OL,8,Fdepots as part of a continuing protest
OL,9,Facross the Republic over rising fuel
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FIreland's justice minister said that
OL,13,Flarge vehicles blocking critical
OL,14,Finfrastructure would be removed.
OL,16,FProtests over the Irish Government's
OL,17,Fresponse to rising fuel prices entered
OL,18,Fa third day on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
