PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FSeveral distinct but co-ordinated
OL,7,Fprotests began on Tuesday involving
OL,8,Fslow-moving convoys on motorways and
OL,9,Fblockades on major roads in Dublin and
OL,10,Fother cities.
OL,12,FHauliers and agricultural contractors
OL,13,Fusing large trucks and tractors are
OL,14,Famong protesters disrupting traffic.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, protests escalated with
OL,17,Fvehicles blocking fuel depots.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
