CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FIn a statement on Thursday morning,
OL,7,FIrish Justice Minister Jim O'Callaghan
OL,8,Fsaid "the blocking of critical
OL,9,Fnational infrastructure will not be
OL,10,Fpermitted to continue and the
OL,11,Fassistance of the Defence Forces has
OL,12,Fbeen requested".
OL,14,FHe added owners of the vehicles
OL,15,Finvolved in the blockades "should
OL,16,Fremove them immediately this morning
OL,17,Fand should not complain later about
OL,18,Fany damage caused to those vehicles
OL,19,Fduring removal".
OL,26,@pD@FOUtD@OO]wD@[OU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FThe Defence Forces confirmed they had
OL,7,Freceived a request for assistance from
OL,8,FAn Garda Siochana and said because
OL,9,F"this operation is ongoing" they would
OL,10,Fnot be commenting further.
OL,12,FThey have four heavy-lift recovery
OL,13,Ftrucks available to help clear trucks
OL,14,Fand tractors involved in blockades and
OL,15,Fit is understood it is envisaged that
OL,16,Fassistance will be limited to these
OL,17,Fvehicles and the personnel required to
OL,18,Foperate them.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FThe Defence Forces also said images of
OL,7,Fa convoy of Mowag armoured personnel
OL,8,Fcarriers circulating on social media
OL,9,Fare "the personnel of the 128th
OL,10,FInfantry Battalion conducting mission
OL,11,Freadiness exercises ahead of
OL,12,Fdeployment to Unifil next month".
OL,14,FThe Irish premier, Micheal Martin,
OL,15,Ftold RTE he did not "anticipate" there
OL,16,Fwould be violence if the army and
OL,17,Fgardai moved in on demonstrators.
OL,19,FThe Taoiseach said it is "not in our
OL,20,Fnature to be engineering any situation
OL,21,Fthat gives rise to conflict".
OL,26,@qD@EOUtD@`O]wD@UOUwD@`O]{D@ZOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
