CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FMr Martin said "the Government had to
OL,7,Fact" once the Whitegate oil refinery
OL,8,Fin Co Cork and the Foynes fuel
OL,9,Fterminal in Co Limerick were blocked.
OL,11,FDefence Minister Helen McEntee told
OL,12,Freporters at the Curragh Camp that the
OL,13,FDefence Forces intervention was "never
OL,14,Fa first resort".
OL,16,FHowever, she said: "It cannot be the
OL,17,Fcase that individuals decide that they
OL,18,Fare going to blockade parts of the
OL,19,Fcountry and stop people from going
OL,20,Fabout their business.
OL,26,@nD@POUoD@DO]uD@aOUvD@OO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,F"That they're going to essentially put
OL,7,Fother businesses out of business now
OL,8,Fbecause of their actions, that farmers
OL,9,Fare potentially going to put animals
OL,10,Fat risk because of their actions, and
OL,11,Fthat people aren't able to get to
OL,12,Fhospital appointments.
OL,14,F"So, as the Government, we have to
OL,15,Ftake firm steps."
OL,17,FFuels for Ireland chief executive
OL,18,FKevin McPartland said forcourts are
OL,19,F"running out of stock" as a "direct
OL,20,Fresult" of blockades.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@QO]{D@AOU{D@VO]{D@]OU|D@
OL,26,AGO]
