PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FMs MacNeill and Ms O'Connor said
OL,7,Faccess was required for emergency
OL,8,Fservices, for patients attending
OL,9,Fmedical appointments and to ensure
OL,10,Fstaff can get to work.
OL,12,FThey said: "Attending hospital or
OL,13,Freceiving treatment in the community,
OL,14,Fwhether in an emergency situation or
OL,15,Ffor a routine appointment, is a
OL,16,Fvulnerable time for a patient and
OL,17,Ftheir family.
OL,26,@tD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
