CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,F"Please respect the critical need for
OL,7,Fclear and safe access to all
OL,8,Fhealthcare services, to ensure that
OL,9,Faccess to care is never compromised."
OL,11,FIn a statement to the media at Garda
OL,12,Fheadquarters in Dublin, Deputy
OL,13,FCommissioner Shawna Coxon said gardai
OL,14,Fare now "moving to an enforcement
OL,15,Fphase" unless protesters "desist and
OL,16,Fdisperse".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]vD@IOUwD@FO]wD@ZOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
