OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FShe added: "An Garda Siochana is
OL,7,Fadvising protesters to immediately
OL,8,Fcease blockades of such critical
OL,9,Fnational infrastructure or face the
OL,10,Ffull rigours of the law."
OL,12,FThe protesters say they have nominated
OL,13,F"three or four" spokespeople they want
OL,14,Fto meet Government leaders.
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@YO]uD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
