OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FHowever, speaking on RTE Radio's
OL,7,FMorning Ireland show, one of them,
OL,8,FJohn Dallon said he does not speak for
OL,9,Fthe protesters blocking fuel depots:
OL,10,F"I'm here on the streets of Dublin, I
OL,11,Fhave no voice as regards what's
OL,12,Fhappening down the country as regards
OL,13,Fblocking up ports."
OL,15,FHe added: "What's happening down there
OL,16,Fis out of my hands, I have no control
OL,17,Fover what happens."
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@SO]wD@KOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
