CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FAgriculture Minister Martin Heydon
OL,7,Fsaid he would meet with farming and
OL,8,Fhaulier representative groups but
OL,9,Fwould not speak to the protesters.
OL,11,FHe said: "What is very clear here is
OL,12,Fthat this is a clear choice between
OL,13,Fdemocracy or anarchy, and we have a
OL,14,Frule of law in this country.
OL,16,F"I completely understand where
OL,17,Fpeople's frustration is from in terms
OL,18,Fof (the) very high energy shock as a
OL,19,Fresult of the war that has broken out
OL,20,Fbetween America, Israel and Iran."
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
