PN,44714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FAsked specifically about the carbon
OL,7,Ftax, which some protesters have
OL,8,Fsuggested should be abolished, Mr
OL,9,FHeydon said: "Undermining the overall
OL,10,Feconomy is not in the best interest of
OL,11,Fthe public at this time, where we're
OL,12,Ffacing a very uncertain geopolitical
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,F"So that's why people have to trust
OL,16,Fthat the Government, while working
OL,17,Fwith all the representative bodies, is
OL,18,Fdoing everything it can within the
OL,19,Fscope of the tools available to us and
OL,20,Fwill continue to examine the
OL,21,Fopportunities further for us."
OL,26,@qD@NOUwD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
