CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FOther coalition figures, including
OL,7,FTanaiste and Finance Minister Simon
OL,8,FHarris, as well as Mr O'Callaghan,
OL,9,Femphasised the importance of access to
OL,10,Ffuel depots and warned of consequences
OL,11,Ffor unlawful activity.
OL,13,FThe cost of petrol, diesel and marked
OL,14,Fgas oil ("green diesel") has soared as
OL,15,Fa result of the war in the Middle East
OL,16,Fand impacts on supplies out of the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@vD@JOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
