OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775826669
OL,3,CThird day of fuel price protests bring
OL,4,CDublin to a standstill
OL,6,FJust over two weeks ago, Ireland's
OL,7,Fruling coalition signed off on a range
OL,8,Fof measures to reduce fuel costs,
OL,9,Fincluding a temporary excise duty
OL,10,Freduction for motor fuels, expansion
OL,11,Fof the diesel rebate scheme for
OL,12,Fhauliers and bus operators, and an
OL,13,Fextension of the fuel allowance.
OL,15,FIt saw an effective reduction of 17
OL,16,Fcents for petrol, 22 cents for diesel,
OL,17,Fand five cents for green diesel ` but
OL,18,Fthe savings were largely eroded as the
OL,19,Fwar raged on.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
